sp.p:
Come, come;
when saw you my father
last?

I am none of these, my lord;
I beseech
your pardon.

I thank thee, fellow;
thou servest
me, and I'll love thee.

Why, no, boy;
nothing can be made
out of nothing.

Marry, here's grace and a cod-piece;
that's a
wise man and a fool.

